pwdx - print process working directory
	pwdx 3315
	3511: /home/cvetomir

lsof -i - print ports and processes that use them
	lsof -i 
	lsof -i :3315 

netstat -tulpn - the netstat tool	

readlink - readlink - print value of a symbolic link or canonical file name

tasksel - a user interface for installing tasks 
